  "text": "Here we have developed an easy-to-use system called CyanoGate that unites cyanobacteria with plant and algal systems, by building on the established Golden Gate MoClo syntax and assembly library for plants [CITATION_1] that has been adopted by the OpenPlant consortium (www.openplant.org), iGEM competitions as \"Phytobricks\" and the MoClo kit for the microalga Chlamydomonas reinhardtii [CITATION_2] .",
